      <title>几内亚比绍领导人在政变企图后解散议会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/guinea-bissau-leader-dissolves-parliament-after-coup-attempt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在国民警卫队成员上周发动政变后，总统乌马罗·西索科·恩巴洛立即解散了国家议会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/guinea-bissau-leader-dissolves-parliament-after-coup-attempt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 17:17:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其警告以色列不要在其领土上杀害哈马斯目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/turkey-warns-israel-against-killing-hamas-targets-on-its-soil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其警告以色列间谍机构不要试图在其领土上杀害哈马斯成员，在有报道称计划在海外暗杀巴勒斯坦激进组织领导人后，土耳其利用秘密渠道传达了这一信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/turkey-warns-israel-against-killing-hamas-targets-on-its-soil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 17:16:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京罕见出访沙特、阿联酋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/putin-to-visit-saudi-arabia-uae-in-rare-trip-abroad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京将前往阿拉伯联合酋长国和沙特阿拉伯，对于这位自入侵乌克兰以来一直面临国际孤立的领导人来说，这是一次罕见的出国访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/putin-to-visit-saudi-arabia-uae-in-rare-trip-abroad</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 17:13:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着保守党压力的增大，苏纳克让获得英国工作签证变得更加困难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/sunak-makes-it-harder-to-get-uk-work-visa-as-tory-pressure-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)政府提高了申请在英国居住的人的工资要求，这是一系列措施之一，旨在向选民表明，他的执政党保守党有计划兑现其在明年大选前减少净移民的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/sunak-makes-it-harder-to-get-uk-work-visa-as-tory-pressure-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 17:03:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院质疑普渡大学阿片类药物协议中的萨克勒盾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/supreme-court-questions-sackler-shield-in-purdue-s-opioid-pact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院暗示，普渡制药公司 60 亿美元阿片类药物和解协议可能存在分歧，因为法官们权衡了拜登政府的论点，即该协议不适当地保护了拥有该公司的萨克勒家族成员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/supreme-court-questions-sackler-shield-in-purdue-s-opioid-pact</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 17:02:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员斯科特质疑佛罗里达州被排除在大学橄榄球季后赛之外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/scott-questions-fsu-s-exclusion-from-college-football-playoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州参议员里克·斯科特周一要求回答为什么大西洋海岸会议冠军佛罗里达州立大学尽管保持不败却没有被选入大学橄榄球季后赛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/scott-questions-fsu-s-exclusion-from-college-football-playoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 16:56:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肖尔茨和卢拉敦促马克龙放弃对欧盟-南方共同市场协议的反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/scholz-lula-urge-macron-to-ditch-opposition-to-eu-mercosur-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国和巴西联手向法国总统马克龙施加压力，要求其放弃对欧盟与四个南美经济体之间达成重大贸易协议的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/scholz-lula-urge-macron-to-ditch-opposition-to-eu-mercosur-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 16:39:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多政府严厉打击石油和天然气甲烷泄漏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/trudeau-government-cracks-down-on-methane-leaks-from-oil-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多政府加强了限制石油和天然气行业甲烷泄漏的法规，履行了在迪拜举行的 COP28 气候峰会上打击破坏性温室气体的重要承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/trudeau-government-cracks-down-on-methane-leaks-from-oil-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 16:37:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行将波兰行长就停职纠纷诉诸欧盟法院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/ecb-says-polish-chief-could-ask-eu-court-to-rule-on-prosecution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，波兰货币政策负责人可能会将任何可能将其停职的行动提交给欧盟最高法院，这表明波兰不愿在不断升级的政治争端中选边站队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/ecb-says-polish-chief-could-ask-eu-court-to-rule-on-prosecution</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 14:17:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列更广泛的战争让美国警惕“战略失败”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/israel-s-expanded-strikes-drive-us-to-warn-of-strategic-defeat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列正在将军事行动扩大到加沙南部，使逃离北部的数十万巴勒斯坦人面临危险，因为美国官员对战争造成的平民伤亡越来越感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/israel-s-expanded-strikes-drive-us-to-warn-of-strategic-defeat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 11:19:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
